#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$
# Superviseur
# Gestion du masque SITRAFIL 

$_AFF
If GIMPORT
 Gosub AFF From GSAISIE
Else
 If GMESSAGE <>""
  Gosub ERR From GSAISIE
 Else
  Raz GERR , GZNUM
 Endif
Endif
Return

$HORODAT
Local Date    A_DATE
Local Char    A_HEURE(10) , A_USER(10)
Local Char    A_STAMP(15)
A_DATE  = [09/11/2018]
A_HEURE = "23:06:29"
A_USER  = "DOC"
A_STAMP = "20181109230629"
Return

$TITRES
Return

$CHG_FMT
Case zoncou
 When "NBCOD"
  If [M]NBCOD=0
  Endif
Endcase
Return

$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask SITRAFIL [SITF]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "SITRAFIL" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [SITF] As [SIM_]
Grizo [SITF]5
Grizo [SITF]15
Grizo [SITF]20
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [SITF]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

$HARDCOP
Local Integer X1(0..14),X2(0..14),Y1(0..14),Y2(0..14)
X1(0)=1 : X2(0)=43 : Y1(0)=1 : Y2(0)=10
X1(1)=44 : X2(1)=84 : Y1(1)=1 : Y2(1)=20
X1(2)=1 : X2(2)=43 : Y1(2)=11 : Y2(2)=14
Return

$ON_CODFIC
Return

$ON_ZCODFIC
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ZCODFIC From W1SITRAFIL
Return

$AV_ZCODFIC
If clalev([F:ATB])=0 : Local File ATABLE [ATB] : Endif
Call LECTURE("ATB",[M]CODFIC(indice),"") From CONTOBJ
Call TEXTE([F:ATB]INTITFIC,zc) From OBJDIV
Gosub _AFF
Return

