$TIT_COL
Local Char TITCL(200)(1..1)
Raz TITCL
Case BASPAG
 When "NBCOD"
  TITCL(1) = mess(GPRODUIT+1,2902,1)
  If !GORITITCOL
   Titcol [M]NBCOD TITCL(1) For X3CLE
  Else
   Titcol [M:SITF]NBCOD TITCL(1) For X3CLE
  Endif
Endcase
Return

